description: NYC DJ, The Loft founder, and Dance legend David Mancuso passed on Nov 14 2016. This is a Tommie Sunshine, Spotify & Billboard Dance tribute. Without Mancuso there would be no Rave scene, no House Music, no festival culture. His legacy is vast; these are merely some of the classics born of The Loft.
